    • build

      public String build()
      Build the final Cypher query.

      Starts with the base query string, appends whatever the optional where function wants, then creates a RETURN clause using the provided function to map fields to strings, and finally adds ORDER BY, SKIP, and LIMIT clauses if necessary.

      Returns:
      final Cypher query
